2. You may **NOT reupload** this mod to other websites, launchers, or download mirrors (including third-party "mod hosting" sites).
3. You may **NOT modify** the mod and publish it under your own name, unless you have written permission.
4. You may **NOT commercialize** the mod in any way (no paywalls, donationware, or selling access).
